[[!meta title="Improve the Tails user interface"]]

You can improve the Tails user interface and user experience.

[[!toc levels=1]]

Known tasks
===========

The tasks marked as [user interface
design](https://labs.riseup.net/code/projects/tails/issues?query_id=123) in
Redmine correspond to things that we would like to see improved in the Tails
user interface.

Other ideas
===========

If you are a UI or HCI person, you can surely find other ideas to improve Tails!
Even if you don't implement your suggestions yourself, [create
tickets](https://labs.riseup.net/code/projects/tails/issues/new) with your ideas
so that others can benefit from your insight.

